    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey friend! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is in absolute pristine, mint condition\u2014seriously, it looks and smells like it just left the showroom floor. It\u2019s been my pride and joy, garage-kept and pampered every single day. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that feels brand new without the brand new price tag, this is definitely the one! Shoot me a message if you want to come see it for yourself!",
