    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine Carbon Black Metallic. This example is powered by the high-revving S54B32 3.2L inline-six, featuring six individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing for a surgical throttle response. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission and a mechanical limited-slip differential, ensuring an unadulterated analog driving experience. This specimen has undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance, including rod bearing replacement and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure chassis longevity. The suspension geometry remains factory-spec, providing exceptional lateral grip and communicative feedback. With its original paint depth and a cabin free of typical bolster wear, this M3 represents the pinnacle of early-2000s German engineering.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
