      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example that defines 'collector quality.' This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, showing no signs of wear. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero rock chips or imperfections, while the factory wheels remain free of any curb rash. Inside, the cabin retains its original showroom scent; the premium leather seats are supple with no bolster wear, and every electronic component functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, it is turn-key, supported by a comprehensive folder of service records from day one. This is not just a used car; it is a time capsule for the discerning buyer who demands perfection.",
